00:06:51.471 --> 00:06:54.554
participating much more in, say, violent acts,

138
00:06:54.554 --> 00:06:56.036
and being arrested much more

139
00:06:56.036 --> 00:06:57.476
than they ever were in history,

140
00:06:57.476 --> 00:06:59.801
in this area of trying to find the power.

141
00:06:59.801 --> 00:07:01.636
Also, at the same time, you have women

