00:27:57.935 --> 00:28:00.405
to try to squelch change because the species

562
00:28:00.405 --> 00:28:02.816
seems to resist change.

563
00:28:02.816 --> 00:28:05.354
<v ->It's been interesting, very interesting historically,</v>

